Package jdraw.std

Class EmptyDrawCommandHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • jdraw.std.EmptyDrawCommandHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DrawCommandHandler
    public class EmptyDrawCommandHandler
extends Object
implements DrawCommandHandler
    Provides an empty command handler. This class provides an empty dummy implementation of the draw command handler. It enables the application to start up correctly and to behave meaningful, but with the limitation that it does not provide any undo/redo behavior.
